<ul>
<li>
BA, BS Degree, or equivalent work experience</li>
<li>
Four years experience in product marketing related function</li>
<li>
Strong understanding of digital advertising space</li>
<li>
Attention to detail and eye for design</li>
<li>
Project management skills and the ability to balance a large number of high priority projects at once</li>
<li>
Passionate about people and talent development</li>
</ul>
